{"tid":1624673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10.6 和理非港島百萬人Sogo集結！最後一日我要見到文宣機器！將遊行捆綁支援中槍手足逼佢地企出嚟！","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:58:35.000Z","uid":167548,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7da78bd142296b0592ac66ca1064877ac6d760","tid":1624673,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zbZUKbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzbZUKbY.jpg&h=824acc80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣手足被射中心口<br />\n元朗手足被射中大腿<br />\n未知手足疑似中實彈<br />\n<br />\n香港人 有得退咩？<br />\n<br />\n星期日我要見到所有自認香港人嘅香港人去港島集結。我發覺有勇武巴打支持18區反對1區，我一叫人去就話推手足去死，呢樣野嘅風險一定要冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一句到尾 兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n老閪都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走唔撚到就唔撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40651d2d48bcf39000f6c6c5f0ef634535b7021","tid":1624673,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"和理非你願意星期日和我一齊上街表達反抗暴政嘅決心？"},{"pid":"e8a97b45e6bcfa7139c25c314223a1a40a754c70","tid":1624673,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"入嚟留言推爆佢"},{"pid":"c2295f2764391e39891d5a35cbe174df77c7dbf1","tid":1624673,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"和理非出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武可以考慮休息/係自己區搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25614c7eae94ef21ed100e16127be23dd805f678","tid":1624673,"uid":101057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"18區開花"},{"pid":"912da97cdf459b2ef58725c7fe4ff4c052709686","tid":1624673,"uid":58803,"like":1,"dislike